## Certification Overview

MCBTA focuses on **threat detection and threat hunting** using ELK/Kibana across real cloud log data from AWS, Azure, and GCP. 30 hands-on challenges required identifying attacker activity from cloud logs — no guided walkthroughs, just raw logs and the task.

